**Rule**: Domain is innermost. Domain code must not import application, infrastructure, or presentation—or **`speech_kit` / `screen_capture_kit`** packages. **Application** orchestrates sibling packages **through infrastructure ports** (recommended) or thin adapters so orchestration logic stays testable.

